sequenceDiagram

    actor User

    participant UI

    participant GoAPI

    participant Storage

    participant DB

    participant AIRuntime

    participant Milvus

    User->>UI: Upload PDF

    UI->>GoAPI: POST /knowledge-sources

    GoAPI->>GoAPI: Validate JWT

    GoAPI->>GoAPI: Check ACL

    GoAPI->>Storage: Upload File

    Storage-->>GoAPI: Object Key

    GoAPI->>DB: Create Knowledge Source

    GoAPI->>DB: Create Ingestion Job

    GoAPI-->>UI: 202 Accepted

    loop Polling

        AIRuntime->>DB: Fetch Pending Job

        DB-->>AIRuntime: Job

        AIRuntime->>Storage: Download PDF

        AIRuntime->>AIRuntime: Parse

        AIRuntime->>AIRuntime: Chunk

        AIRuntime->>AIRuntime: Embedding

        AIRuntime->>Milvus: Store Vector

        AIRuntime->>DB: Update Job

        AIRuntime->>DB: Update Knowledge Source

    end